articles.title: 2nd Test, Day 3: Australia remove Rachin Ravindra, Daryl Mitchell but New Zealand charge on - Hindustan Times
articles.description: After resuming the day at 134-2, New Zealand are having a productive batting session against Australia. | Cricket
articles.content: Australia claimed the wickets of Rachin Ravindra and Daryl Mitchell but failed to stem the New Zealand run flow in the middle session Sunday on day three of the second Test. Hosts New Zealand were 34… [+1679 chars]
